place.name: ST MARY IN THE MARSH
place.gazetteerText: St Mary the Virgin.-- coast par., Kent, in Romney Marsh, 2 miles N. of New Romney, 1916 ac., pop. 185. (In 1887, John Bartholomew's Gazetteer of the British Isles)
